CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five men, including Pittsburgh Councilman Paul F. Jones and Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence presenting key, standing in the Office of the Mayor at the City County Building
